        <p>"I'd quit smoking, I was doing everything right, but every morning I'd wake up feeling like I was breathing through a wet blanket."</p>
        <p>That changed about eight months ago, when Gary ran into a pharmacist at a local health expo in Knoxville.</p>
        <p>The pharmacist had spent years researching traditional herbal remedies for respiratory wellness.</p>
